title: Abt Quick Tips: Back To School Laptops
description:
Heading back to campus? This video highlights a few different laptops that we carry at Abt. Whether you need a powerhouse gaming laptop or something to get you through your basic GenEd classes we have something for everyone!  

MSI GE72 Apache Aluminum Gaming Laptop - http://www.abt.com/product/92657/MSI-GE72APACHE078.html

Apple MacBook Pro 13.3 With Retina Display - http://www.abt.com/product/89685/Apple-MF840LLA.html

Lenovo ThinkPad E550 - http://www.abt.com/product/89736/Lenovo-20DF0030US.html

Asus Chromebook Flip C100 - http://www.abt.com/product/93296/ASUS-C100PADB02.html
